      <title>特朗普弗里德曼（Floats Floats Floats Floats）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-floats-friedman-grenell-as-possible-picks-for-un-envoy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统浮动了前美国驻以色列戴维·弗里德曼（David Friedman）和特使里克·格雷内尔（Ric Grenell）作为联合国大使的潜在选秀权，此前一个狭窄的众议院共和党多数派撤销了代表埃利斯·斯特凡尼克（Elise Stefanik）的提名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-floats-friedman-grenell-as-possible-picks-for-un-envoy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:41:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，普京将“跟进”，拒绝乌克兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-putin-will-follow-through-rebuffs-ukraine-on-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）表示，他相信俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）将遵循达成一项停火协议，并指控乌克兰试图与美国谈判经济协议，以最新的转折，以谈判在正在进行的冲突中谈判临时停战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-putin-will-follow-through-rebuffs-ukraine-on-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:34:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚反对派希望银行监管机构释放贷款标准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/australia-opposition-wants-bank-regulator-to-ease-loan-standards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的中央反对派将敦促美国的银行监管机构缓解其抵押贷款标准，以便允许更多的人在下个月赢得办公室的情况下借用房屋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/australia-opposition-wants-bank-regulator-to-ease-loan-standards</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，勒庞定罪是“大事”，与他的案件类似</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-le-pen-conviction-is-big-deal-similar-to-his-cases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）因挪用公款被定罪，并将其法律困境比作他在夺回权力之前所面临的起诉后，为极右翼法国领导人马林·勒庞（Marine Le Pen）提供了支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-says-le-pen-conviction-is-big-deal-similar-to-his-cases</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:26:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
