    <item>
      <title>USTR Greer计划下周捍卫特朗普对国会的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/ustr-greer-slated-to-defend-trump-tariffs-to-congress-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士说，美国贸易代表杰米森·格里尔（Jamieson Greer）将于下周在国会上作证，就在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布预计将是一项大量关税议程之后的几天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/ustr-greer-slated-to-defend-trump-tariffs-to-congress-next-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 22:26:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普创建投资办公室来监督芯片法案资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-creates-investment-office-to-administer-chips-act-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统签署了一项行政命令，以在商务部内建立办事处，以促进和加快在美国超过10亿美元的投资，并根据《筹码和科学法》管理联邦资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-creates-investment-office-to-administer-chips-act-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 21:45:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国汽车制造商大厅将低成本零件排除在关税之外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-automakers-lobby-to-exclude-low-cost-car-parts-from-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士说，美国汽车制造商正在游说特朗普政府将某些车辆零件排除在关税之外，这是在本周开始生效之前在他们开始生效之前要影响征费的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/us-automakers-lobby-to-exclude-low-cost-car-parts-from-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 21:32:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普针对门票剥皮，新行政命令的费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-to-target-ticket-scalping-fees-with-new-executive-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周一签署了一项行政命令，旨在打破票务剥头和费用，以增加参加消费者现场活动的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/trump-to-target-ticket-scalping-fees-with-new-executive-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 20:42:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
